    "ARCHITECTURE OF PRE-TRAINED MODELS IN IMAGE CLASSIFICATION A. ResNet (Residual Networks)Microsoft Research introduced Residual Network architecture with the proposal of ResNet [4].",
    "The idea of residual blocks was introduced in this architecture to address the issue of the vanishing/exploding gradient.",
    "Skip connections are a method that are employed in this network Table II.",
    "By skipping some layers in between, the skip connection links a layer's activations to other layers.",
    "This creates a block that remains."
  ]
}